title: Long.Way.Down.S01E05.WS.PDTV.XviD-REMAX
description:
Ewan McGregor and Charley Boorman get up close to Africa\&#039;s wildlife as 
   they spot zebras in Kenya and view Rwanda\&#039;s mountain gorillas in their 
   natural habitat. Emotions are running high as they pay a visit to a 
   Unicef site for former child soldiers in northern Uganda, and one of the
   duo looks forward to getting out of Tanzania, as it means he\&#039;ll be 
   reunited with a loved one
